page.title: 08MY WEEKEND
page.content:
My name is wayne milner.I am 11 years old.In my spare time I like working at my dads garage washing cars and cleaning them out.I get 1 pound a car.I normally clean 10 cars a week. I also like bike rides,sometimes i go down to colwick park.My favourite food is chicken,chips and beans.I collect badges.I go to bed at 10.00 pm on school days.My favourite colour is green.My dad is a car mechanic.My mum works at Ladbrokes .I have a sister aged 4.Once a year they have a fair on the Forum.It is a rip off,50p a ride .At times i go to the fair for a couple of hours.Iam aways around when they set the fair up.
by wayne milner.
